snippet.title: Survival Story Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Release on September 26 in Steam
Survival Story is a zombie-infested world where every step can be the last. Look for food and water, hunt and craft, and find out all the secrets that this world hides. Can you survive in a harsh world where everyone wants to kick your ass?
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2878060/Survival_Story/
